-	The buffer_subbuf_order allows the user to change the size of the sub
-	buffer. As the sub buffer is a set of pages by the power of 2, thus
-	the sub buffer total size is defined by the order:
-
-	order		size
-	----		----
-	0		PAGE_SIZE
